    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> 36 lines of test for 2 (with a blank line) of fix. GG 👍\r\n\r\nShould we export the refinement methods and only test them to avoid having to set a complex fixture to do a one line change?\r\n\r\nAs soon as we have a stable codebase like now (where we know we will have those refine methods for long), we could test those refine methods by units rather than having to render a full widget.\r\n\r\n(thinking out loud)",
